Linus Bootstrap: Multistage initialization process during booting a linux installation.
1. BIOS
2. MBR
3. GRUB
4. KERNEL
5. INIT
6. RUNLEVEL
--------------------------------
RUN-LEVEL
0 - shutdown
1 - single user
2 - multiuser
3 - multiuser with n/w
4 - Not used
5 - GUI
6 - Reboot
