----------------------------: CRON-JOB :-------------------
Five astricts - * * * * *
* mins in hour
* hour in day
* day in month
* month in year
* [ 0,7:Sunday, 1:Monday ]
Ex:
 to list crontab entries: crontab -l
 sunday @ 5pm: * 17 * * 0 sample.sh

---------------------------: FOLDER STRUCTURE :-------------
- /root :root user home directory
- /etc :configuration files , backup files
- /home :other user home directory
- /bin :binary files(mainly cmnds present within /bin, both normal & root user can be use)
- /sbin
- /dev
- /lib
- /lib64
- /tmp
- /opt
- /boot
